        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         That is the same thing with fear.  When I used to only fear kite with dread gaze staff I learned real quick to let the fear run it's course and start to recast about the time invoke would wear off if it went it's full duration.  Too many times when I chain casted invoke the mob would break fear a second or two after I had landed it.  So if the charm/fear or whatever seems to be going without a hitch no reason to risk letting it break early by constantly recasting the spell.</P><P><center><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=230113" target="_blank"><b>Sokul</b></a><BR>Avengers Federation</center><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
